OL,3,CMan who smashed police van and left
OL,4,Cofficer 'fearing for life' jailed
OL,6,FA dad has been jailed after battering
OL,7,Fa police van with a slab of concrete -
OL,8,Fleaving the officer inside frightened
OL,9,Ffor his life.
OL,11,FLuke Moran, 38, attempted to pull the
OL,12,Fwing mirror off the van before
OL,13,F"forcefully punching" the window and
OL,14,Fsmashing it with masonry, trapping PC
OL,15,FJames Hayes inside.
OL,17,FThe dad-of-three was one of hundreds
OL,18,Finvolved in rioting in Southport after
OL,19,Fviolence erupted following the deaths
OL,20,Fof three girls in a knife attack.
