OL,3,CMan who smashed police van and left
OL,4,Cofficer 'fearing for life' jailed
OL,6,FRebecca Smith, prosecuting, told
OL,7,FLiverpool Crown Court Moran was seen
OL,8,Fon footage with a large piece of
OL,9,Fconcrete in his hands, smashing the
OL,10,Fdriver's side window of a police
OL,11,Fvehicle.
OL,13,FJailing him, Judge Neil Flewitt KC
OL,14,Ftold the court: "This is as bad a case
OL,15,Fas I have seen so far."
OL,17,FHe said serious disorder, in the form
OL,18,Fof vandalism, intimidation and
OL,19,Fviolence, broke out in Merseyside and
OL,20,Facross the country following the fatal
OL,21,Fstabbing in Southport on July 29th.
