OL,3,CMan who smashed police van and left
OL,4,Cofficer 'fearing for life' jailed
OL,6,FOn July 30th a "mob" formed in
OL,7,FSouthport, initially focused on the
OL,8,Flocal mosque, and there were chants of
OL,9,F"Allah, Allah, who the f*** is Allah"
OL,10,Fand "this is our f****** country", the
OL,11,Fjudge said.
OL,13,FThe court was played bodyworn footage
OL,14,Ffrom PC Hayes in which Moran was
OL,15,Fholding a chunk of masonry, which he
OL,16,Fhit the vehicle with three times.
OL,18,FIn the footage, the constable could be
OL,19,Fheard telling colleagues over his
OL,20,Fradio: "I'm going to have to bail, my
OL,21,Fwindow's about to go through."
