OL,3,CMan who smashed police van and left
OL,4,Cofficer 'fearing for life' jailed
OL,6,FIn a statement, PC Hayes said he was
OL,7,Fleft fearing for his safety.
OL,9,FHe said: "My carrier became isolated
OL,10,Fand a focal point of the ongoing
OL,11,Fbarrage.
OL,13,F"I seriously feared for my safety as I
OL,14,Fwas faced by hundreds of men
OL,15,Fattempting to inflict serious harm
OL,16,Fonto the police.
OL,18,F"There was an obvious 'hardcore'
OL,19,Felement of the mob which stood at the
OL,20,Ffront of the crowd who were intent on
OL,21,Finflicting harm on officers."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
