OL,3,CMan who smashed police van and left
OL,4,Cofficer 'fearing for life' jailed
OL,6,FMoran, from Birkdale, Merseyside, was
OL,7,Fone of a crowd of people throwing
OL,8,Fmissiles, bins and other items at
OL,9,Fofficers and police vehicles in
OL,10,FSouthport after violence erupted
OL,11,Ffollowing a vigil for Elsie Dot
OL,12,FStancombe, six, Bebe King, seven, and
OL,13,FAlice de Silva Aguia, nine.
OL,15,FThe girls were killed when a knifeman
OL,16,Fentered their Taylor Swift-themed
OL,17,Fdance class and began attacking the
OL,18,Fgroup.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
