OL,3,CMan who smashed police van and left
OL,4,Cofficer 'fearing for life' jailed
OL,6,FCCTV showed Moran in the crowd on
OL,7,FZetland Street before the attack,
OL,8,Fmilling around and appearing to incite
OL,9,Fthe disorder which was near to the
OL,10,Fmosque in Southport.
OL,12,FHe then approached the stationary
OL,13,Fpolice van, where a police officer was
OL,14,Fat the wheel.
OL,16,FA bodycam worn by the officer in the
OL,17,Fvan captured Moran's attack, and he
OL,18,Fwas later arrested after being
OL,19,Fidentified from the CCTV footage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
