OL,3,CMan who smashed police van and left
OL,4,Cofficer 'fearing for life' jailed
OL,6,FHis response to questions during
OL,7,Fpolice interview was: "I was nowhere
OL,8,Fnear Zetland Street, St Luke's Street,
OL,9,Fmate."
OL,11,FJailing Moran for three years Judge
OL,12,FFlewitt said: "Unsurprisingly... PC
OL,13,FHayes feared for his life, believing
OL,14,Fhe might be pulled from the carrier
OL,15,Fand attacked."
