OL,3,CMan who smashed police van and left
OL,4,Cofficer 'fearing for life' jailed
OL,6,FThe arrest was part of the police
OL,7,Finvestigation into the violent
OL,8,Fdisorder that occurred from 30 July
OL,9,F2024 onwards, in the aftermath of the
OL,10,Ftragic deaths of three young girls,
OL,11,Fmurdered in Southport the previous day.
OL,13,FMoran appeared in the dock with three
OL,14,Fother defendants, who fist bumped and
OL,15,Fsaid "good luck" to each other before
OL,16,Fthe sentencing began.
OL,18,FFamily members of all four defendants
OL,19,Fwere in tears as the sentences were
OL,20,Fdelivered.
