OL,3,CMan who smashed police van and left
OL,4,Cofficer 'fearing for life' jailed
OL,6,FMoran's friend Nicholas Sinclair, 38,
OL,7,Fa manager at a scaffolding firm,
OL,8,Fappeared alongside him in the dock on
OL,9,FWednesday and was jailed for two years
OL,10,Fand four months.
OL,12,FThe court heard Sinclair, of Bury
OL,13,FRoad, Birkdale, was seen in footage
OL,14,Ffrom the disorder shouting towards
OL,15,Fpolice and throwing bricks.
OL,17,FSimon Christie, defending both men,
OL,18,Fsaid they had been "swept up in an
OL,19,Fincident they neither understood or
OL,20,Ftook the time to consider".
