OL,3,CMan who smashed police van and left
OL,4,Cofficer 'fearing for life' jailed
OL,6,FJudge Flewitt said: "Everybody so far
OL,7,Fhas said they were swept up in the
OL,8,Fviolence, nobody seems to be taking
OL,9,Fresponsibility."
OL,11,FHe added: "It was neither thoughtless
OL,12,Fnor mindless, it was deliberate."
OL,14,FBoth men had pleaded guilty to violent
OL,15,Fdisorder at Liverpool Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt last week.
