OL,6,FSentenced alongside them were Daniel
OL,7,FCarrigan, 41, of Preston Grove in
OL,8,FLiverpool, who was jailed for two
OL,9,Fyears and eight months for violent
OL,10,Fdisorder and criminal damage and
OL,11,FThomas Whitehead, 53, of Pool Street
OL,12,FSouthport, who was sentenced to one
OL,13,Fyear and eight months for violent
OL,14,Fdisorder.
