OL,3,CMan who smashed police van and left
OL,4,Cofficer 'fearing for life' jailed
OL,6,FDistrict Crown Prosecutor Sarah Gray,
OL,7,Fof CPS Mersey Cheshire, said: "The
OL,8,Ffootage of Moran battering at the
OL,9,Fpolice van door is truly shocking, it
OL,10,Fmade it impossible for the officer to
OL,11,Feither drive away or get out - the
OL,12,Flevel of violence and aggression used
OL,13,Fabsolutely appalling.
OL,15,F"In the midst of the serious violent
OL,16,Fdisorder Moran persists in battering
OL,17,Fthe door and seems absolutely
OL,18,Fdetermined to try to get at the
OL,19,Fofficer.
OL,26,@oD@_OU
